375
00:30:26,532 --> 00:30:30,566
Adakah anda mempunyai sebarang cadangan?

376
00:30:33,933 --> 00:30:35,754
Pengesyoran, anda katakan...

377
00:30:36,587 --> 00:30:39,873
Stik lidah lembu dan skirt kami
